Package curam.util.client.domain.compare

Contains functionality that allows the comparison of homogeneous values when sorting and therefore controls the sort order of the data displayed on list pages.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DomainComparator A comparator interface for domain data.
 

Class Summary
AbstractComparator An abstract super-class for domain comparator classes.
CodeTableCodeCaseInsensitiveComparator A comparator for the code-table domains.
CodeTableCodeComparator A comparator for the code-table domains.
CodeTableCodeLocaleAwareComparator A comparator for the code-table domains.
CuramTimeComparator A comparator for the CURAM_TIME domain a sub-domain of the SVR_DATETIME domain represented by the curam.util.type.DateTime class, but for this domain, the date part is not considered significant for the comparison.
SvrBlobComparator A comparator for the SVR_BLOB domain represented by the curam.util.type.Blob class.
SvrBooleanComparator A comparator for the SVR_BOOLEAN domain.
SvrCharComparator A comparator for the SVR_CHAR domain.
SvrDateComparator A comparator for the SVR_DATE domain represented by the curam.util.type.Date class.
SvrDateTimeComparator A comparator for the SVR_DATETIME domain represented by the curam.util.type.DateTime class.
SvrDoubleComparator A comparator for the SVR_DOUBLE domain.
SvrFloatComparator A comparator for the SVR_FLOAT domain.
SvrInt16Comparator A comparator for the SVR_INT16 domain.
SvrInt32Comparator A comparator for the SVR_INT32 domain.
SvrInt64Comparator A comparator for the SVR_INT64 domain.
SvrInt8Comparator A comparator for the SVR_INT8 domain.
SvrMoneyComparator A comparator for the SVR_MONEY domain represented by the curam.util.type.Money class.
SvrStringCaseInsensitiveComparator A comparator for the SVR_STRING and SVR_UNBOUNDED_STRING domains.
SvrStringComparator A comparator for the SVR_STRING and SVR_UNBOUNDED_STRING domains.
SvrStringLocaleAwareComparator A locale-aware comparator for the SVR_STRING and SVR_UNBOUNDED_STRING domains.
 

Package curam.util.client.domain.compare Description

Contains functionality that allows the comparison of homogeneous values when sorting and therefore controls the sort order of the data displayed on list pages.
